        "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_CYBORG2_GRANDMASTERY_DESC": "As Cyborg, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon.",
        "SS2_KEYWORD_GOUGE2": "<style=cKeywordName>Gouge</style><style=cSub>Applies 100% damage over time. Capable of critical hits and activating item effects.",
